original_title: Parade of Mystic Shriners, Luna Park, Coney Island
overview: A convention of the fraternal order of Shriners was the subject of this film, photographed at Luna Park in Coney Island, New York. During the film, members of the organization can be seen passing the camera position on camels or horses, in horse-drawn vehicles, or walking. All members of the parading group were attired in some sort of distinguishing regalia.
title: Parade of Mystic Shriners, Luna Park, Coney Island
